title: Cheesy Pulled Pork & Bacon Toastie with Shoestring Fries, Spicy Pickles & Aioli
description: Get ready for the ultimate comfort food mash-up with this twist on a classic cheese toastie! Stacked with melty Cheddar and a decadent mix of BBQ pulled pork and bacon, it’s a flavour-packed, crunchy, saucy ride.
